org.team5940.pantry.logging.messages

Class BaseMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.team5940.pantry.logging.messages.Message
      • org.team5940.pantry.logging.messages.BaseMessage

  • public class BaseMessage
extends Message
    A BaseMessage is a Message with only very basic metadata that all logs use. The metadata that is stored includes time, runtime, thread, and source.

    • Constructor Summary

      BaseMessage(java.lang.Object source)
